      <tbody><tr>
        <td width="100%" height="53px" bgcolor="#0b0c0c">
          <table width="580" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" align="center">
            <tbody><tr>
              <td width="100%" bgcolor="#0b0c0c" valign="middle"> 
                <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0">
                  <tbody><tr>
                    <td width="26"><img src="https://c.cs83.content.force.com/servlet/servlet.ImageServer?id=0154E000000DYOT&oid=00D4E0000008r45" alt="Companies House Crest" style="width: 48px; height: 40px; display:block;"></td>
                    <td width="7"><img src="https://c.cs83.content.force.com/servlet/servlet.ImageServer?id=0154E000000DYOY&oid=00D4E0000008r45" alt="" width="7px" height="26px" style="display: block;"></td>
                    <td style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">
                      <h2 class="organisation-logo" style="font-size: 27px; line-height: 20px; font-weight: 300; margin: 0; color: #FFFFFF;"><span>Companies House</span></h2>
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </tbody></table>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </tbody></table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </tbody></table>
    <table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" bgcolor="#FFFFFF">
      <tbody><tr>
        <td width="100%">
          <table width="580" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" align="center" style="border-top: 10px solid #005EA5;">
            <tbody><tr>
              <td width="100%" style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"><h1 class="email" style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 48px; line-height: 1.041666667; margin: 30px 0;">Request  to close {!Transaction__c.CompanyName__c}</h1></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td width="100%" style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;">
                <p style="font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.315789474; margin: 0 0 30px 0;">
                A request to close {!Transaction__c.CompanyName__c}({!Transaction__c.CompanyNumber__c}) whose registered office address is {!Transaction__c.CompanyAddress1__c}  {!Transaction__c.CompanyPostCode__c} <b>needs your approval</b> before it can be submitted to Companies House for processing. 
        
                </br> </br>
                The request will be deleted if it's not approved and completed by {!Today()+90}. Your reference number for any future enquiries is FE{!Transaction__c.Id}. </p>

                <h2 style="font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.315789474; margin: 0 0 30px 0;">What happens next</h2>

                <p style="font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.315789474; margin: 0 0 30px 0;">
                Once the request has been approved by all individuals required, we will email you with instructions for you to review, complete and submit the request.</a> </p>

                <p style="font-size: 19px; line-height: 1.315789474; margin: 0 0 30px 0;">
                It is the responsibility of directors to ensure that copies of the request have been sent to all interested parties. This can include members (usually shareholders), creditors and employees, who must be notified within 7 days of submitting the completed request. The full list of who to tell can be found in the <a href='https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/company-strike-off-dissolution-and-restoration'>online guide.</a> </p>
                

              </td>
            </tr>
          </tbody></table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </tbody></table>
  
